columns.name: name
columns.description: The name that you specified when traffic policy was created.

columns.name: id
columns.description: The ID that Amazon Route 53 assigned to a traffic policy when it was created.

columns.name: type
columns.description: The DNS type of the resource record sets that Amazon Route 53 creates when you use a traffic policy to create a traffic policy instance.

columns.name: version
columns.description: The version number that Amazon Route 53 assigns to a traffic policy.

columns.name: comment
columns.description: The comment that you specified when traffic policy was created.

columns.name: document
columns.description: The definition of a traffic policy in JSON format.
